cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark, please cite it as below."
title: "Adversarial Reasoning Attacks on Medical Imaging VLM Agents"
abstract: >-
  A publication-grade benchmark measuring how white-box image-space adversarial
  perturbations alter the reasoning trajectories (tool-call sequences, tool
  parameters, task success) of open-source Vision-Language Model agents in a
  medical imaging context, with HF fp16 → Ollama Q4 transfer evaluation.
